        "type": "game",
        "name": "Backrooms: Escape Together",
        "steam_appid": 2141730,
        "required_age": 0,
        "is_free": false,
        "short_description": "A visually lifelike co-op horror game for 1-6 people. Journey through 11 procedurally generated levels, using what's available to survive and progress deeper into the Backrooms.",
        "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b1ed74a9d6f96535ccf98534dd1c43e2.avif?t=1780282746\" alt=\"Survive with friends.\" width=1170 height=90 /></span>Play alone, or team up with friends <i>(or strangers!)</i> in up to <strong>6-player co-op</strong>. Enjoy hilarious moments as you watch them die from the horrors you encounter, as <strong>proximity voice chat</strong> carries their screams down the halls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/14e30a3ea6cdc36f6a25b172fe89c650.poster.avif?t=1780282746\" aria-label=\"Gameplay clip showing players exploring the Backrooms together.\" width=1170 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/14e30a3ea6cdc36f6a25b172fe89c650.webm?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/14e30a3ea6cdc36f6a25b172fe89c650.mp4?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/36cf0389d71a8574892d87c991069bcb.avif?t=1780282746\" alt=\"Dangerous entities.\" width=1170 height=90 /></span>Encounter dangerous entities from across the Backrooms as you push deeper through each level. Each entity has its own behavior and way of hunting the player. Learn what they react to and how to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/2e82c215314dd035390436c3cae864bd.poster.avif?t=1780282746\" aria-label=\"Gameplay clip showing a dangerous entity encounter in the Backrooms.\" width=1170 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/2e82c215314dd035390436c3cae864bd.webm?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/2e82c215314dd035390436c3cae864bd.mp4?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/4ff3f3ca262639df7b4286ab6200e47c.avif?t=1780282746\" alt=\"Life like immersion.\" width=1170 height=90 /></span>Explore <strong>photorealistic environments</strong>, handcrafted to feel unsettling. Life like visuals and <strong>spatialized audio</strong> remove all barriers between you and the game. Start in the yellow halls of Level 0 as you descend deeper into the Backrooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b1a10b6780d1cc476357fe4f5a464418.poster.avif?t=1780282746\" aria-label=\"Gameplay clip showing a player running through the Backrooms as red lights flash and an alarm blares.\" width=1170 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b1a10b6780d1cc476357fe4f5a464418.webm?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b1a10b6780d1cc476357fe4f5a464418.mp4?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/73388b91862cb2a38c0c753930588e39.avif?t=1780282746\" alt=\"Every run changes.\" width=1170 height=90 /></span>Every level brings its own environment, mechanics, and threats to survive. Even within the same level, each attempt brings different layouts, item spawns, and entity encounters. No two runs are the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/614632051020c95d056db30f6c68a51e.poster.avif?t=1780282746\" aria-label=\"Gameplay clip showing a player dropping through a hole in the party room.\" width=1170 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/614632051020c95d056db30f6c68a51e.webm?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/614632051020c95d056db30f6c68a51e.mp4?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/b03de1c5c7666b279760378e52960497.avif?t=1780282746\" alt=\"The most realistic Backrooms experience.\" width=1170 height=90 /></span>Backrooms: Escape Together is a co-op survival horror game featuring lifelike graphics, proximity voice chat, and horrifying entities. You and up to 5 friends must make your way through 11 fully procedurally generated levels using what's available to you to progress deeper into the Backrooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every level is a mini-adventure of its own, hosting unique gameplay, puzzles, lootable items, environments, and entities. Levels will be added constantly throughout Early Access as we grow the game into the best multiplayer experience to date.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/261591f25167edb1108439ddc124c871.poster.avif?t=1780282746\" aria-label=\"Gameplay clip showing three friends dancing together in the Backrooms.\" width=1170 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/261591f25167edb1108439ddc124c871.webm?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2141730/extras/261591f25167edb1108439ddc124c871.mp4?t=1780282746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
